{"tid":1834512,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"[賭波]  越分析得深入，越覺得冇路捉","createTime":"2020-01-22T11:58:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-22T17:34:14.000Z","uid":123335,"like":20,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"07d57ca5ab71e896e7be00987e231d619ebdfff5","tid":1834512,"uid":123335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T11:58:08.000Z","msg":"你地覺得自己會中<br />\n只不過係因為你地分析得未夠深入<br />\n<br />\n其實果啲初盤、尾盤、兩隊近績 ...etc 等考慮因素<br />\n都只係時跟時唔跟，唔會有路捉 <br />\n覺得捉到路既人，多數患有：<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>「選擇性失憶症」</strong></span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你諗下你果個 strategy 係咪一直以來都 works ? <br />\n還是只係近幾場中左，就導致心雄？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實，<br />\n你贏錢唔代表你聰明醒目<br />\n只不過係代表你有運 <br />\n<strong>其實有好多賭仔都睇唔透成個大局觀</strong> <br />\n<br />\n我唔會叫大家戒賭 <br />\n<strong>&ldquo; Risk is what makes us young &ldquo; </strong> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你出街搭地鐵，都難保隔離咳緊果個呀叔有武漢肺炎<br />\n就算係condom，都唔係100% 避孕 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n風險嘅嘢無處不在，亦都係呢個世界有趣既地方<br />\n<br />\n做人最重要係識<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">「控制風險」</span></strong><br />\n小賭怡情、刀仔鋸大樹<br />\n感受下命運受到蹉跎<br />\n為生活增添色彩<br />\n此生無憾 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b28b8212526a648ef0d296340b19a5603cc5e74c","tid":1834512,"uid":228475,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T11:59:02.000Z","msg":"買波與彪同行更安心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09615ddb1bb746a8913b487b073e3d096cce2f08","tid":1834512,"uid":135959,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T11:59:10.000Z","msg":"Newcastle 90&rsquo;+4<br />\nNewcastle 90&rsquo;+5"},{"pid":"abe78729e3e9ac5dfdd3c97adc1bb48683c9280f","tid":1834512,"uid":228475,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"09615ddb1bb746a8913b487b073e3d096cce2f08","tid":1834512,"uid":135959,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T11:59:10.000Z","msg":"Newcastle 90&rsquo;+4<br />\nNewcastle 90&rsquo;+5"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T11:59:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c525ad5b2a9e1ba993b5efa967125157984006e4","tid":1834512,"uid":17516,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T12:06:15.000Z","msg":"連贏個時就會話<br />\n睇晒d 盤點點 捉到路<br />\n懶係分析晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一斷就話轉咗操盤手/莊家點點點"},{"pid":"9e7ca8d2a8f3a301cefbcd4078ae3776fb2ac929","tid":1834512,"uid":73241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T12:08:44.000Z","msg":"bill gor<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d45866fa1a05b2346942ce7397ea9ccbad71f9a8","tid":1834512,"uid":123335,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"c525ad5b2a9e1ba993b5efa967125157984006e4","tid":1834512,"uid":17516,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T12:06:15.000Z","msg":"連贏個時就會話<br />\n睇晒d 盤點點 捉到路<br />\n懶係分析晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一斷就話轉咗操盤手/莊家點點點"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T12:09:05.000Z","msg":"賭仔輸果陣就會話：<strong>「個莊轉左手法操盤」</strong><br />\n<br />\n我心諗：<br />\n<strong>「點解唔可以面對現實，承認自己輸運呢 」</strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e7e8f210